Reference material
------------------

The mechanism of session capture was studied from PostHog/posthog-android
(MIT License) and the wire contract from PostHog/posthog
(rr-mobile-schema.json). This SDK is a clean-room reimplementation against
SPEC.md; no PostHog source files were copied verbatim. Nothing under PostHog's
`ee/` directory was referenced.

